### 建立報價 (POST)
POST http://localhost:3000/quotations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "你的customerId",
  "createdById": "你的userId",
  "items": [
    {
      "productName": "Workerz Exit 工具腰包",
      "qty": 2,
      "unitPrice": 1500,
      "discountRate": 10
    }
  ]
}

### 查全部報價 (GET)
GET http://localhost:3000/quotations

### 查單筆報價 (GET)
GET http://localhost:3000/quotations/e42caaf5-ada5-41c0-98a3-be5eec384e49

### 更新報價狀態 (PATCH - DRAFT → SENT)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/quotations/e42caaf5-ada5-41c0-98a3-be5eec384e49/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SENT"
}